#include <iostream>

using namespace std;

int min(int, int);
int max(int, int);

main()
{
int fall, l1, r1, o1, u1, l2, r2, o2, u2, lx, rx, ox,ux;

cin >> fall;
while(fall--)
	{
	cin >> l1 >> u1 >> r1 >> o1;
	cin >> l2 >> u2 >> r2 >> o2;

	if(l2>=r1 || l1>=r2 || u2>=o1 || u1>=o2)
		cout << "No Overlap" << endl;
	else
		{
		lx=max(l1,l2);
		rx=min(r1,r2);
		ox=min(o1,o2);
		ux=max(u1,u2);
		cout << lx << " " << ux << " " << rx << " " << ox << endl;
		}
	}

return 0;
}

int min(int a, int b)
{
if(a<b)
	return a;
else
	return b;
}

int max(int a, int b)
{
if(a>b)
	return a;
else
	return b;
}
